					<description><![CDATA[I have been working out with my own free weights and other minor home equipment at least 3 times a week for years now; this year I have taken on a version of Dean Ornish&#039;s Reversal Diet under the supervision of my holistic doctor who does blood draws about every 3 months or so.  He made it still more difficult at the beginning by denying most fruit and gluten.  I have since told him (after the 1st trimester) that I took back the gluten and some fruits (although I still try to limit my use of sweet ones like banana, pineapple).  I also have about an OZ of dark chocolate (70-90% cocoa)daily.  And I use the sweetener Stevia in my morning lime juice (and cocoa the few times I have made that with unsweetened almond milk).  I drink that milk or thinned V8 with meals and sometimes have a snack of 1/4 C of plain Greek Yogurt (Voskos is yummy).  I will put moderate amounts of low-fat meat and cheese in my meals after next February (1 year).  I need to find a site where I can search for a local lover by describing what I want of his anatomy.  I have been very good friends with someone very special and we were together last year (as I traveled for my daughter&#039;s 3rd wedding) and we enjoyed a better honeymoon (we think) than the kids.  I am still active in my arts and crafts (retired from engineering) with many friends but those other needs are deeper.]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>I have been working out with my own free weights and other minor home equipment at least 3 times a week for years now; this year I have taken on a version of Dean Ornish&#8217;s Reversal Diet under the supervision of my holistic doctor who does blood draws about every 3 months or so.  He made it still more difficult at the beginning by denying most fruit and gluten.  I have since told him (after the 1st trimester) that I took back the gluten and some fruits (although I still try to limit my use of sweet ones like banana, pineapple).  I also have about an OZ of dark chocolate (70-90% cocoa)daily.  And I use the sweetener Stevia in my morning lime juice (and cocoa the few times I have made that with unsweetened almond milk).  I drink that milk or thinned V8 with meals and sometimes have a snack of 1/4 C of plain Greek Yogurt (Voskos is yummy).  I will put moderate amounts of low-fat meat and cheese in my meals after next February (1 year).  I need to find a site where I can search for a local lover by describing what I want of his anatomy.  I have been very good friends with someone very special and we were together last year (as I traveled for my daughter&#8217;s 3rd wedding) and we enjoyed a better honeymoon (we think) than the kids.  I am still active in my arts and crafts (retired from engineering) with many friends but those other needs are deeper.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
		
